frontmatter.bio: I am an undergraduate student majoring in computer science and am an aspiring web developer. I love exploring the latest technologies and am currently looking into DevOps and Blockchain in general. I joined Layer5 as a contributor back in July 2021, and it has been one of my best experiences contributing to an open-source project.
